  <div class="sg-section">
    <a name="simple-form"></a>
    <h2>Form Type</h2>
    <a name="forms"></a>
    <h3>Simple Form</h3>
    <p>Forms require a few sections to work correctly.  Form items need to be inside a <code>&lt;form class=&quot;form-content&quot;&gt;</code> section.  Form groups (label and form-control pair) need to be inside a section with <code>.form-section</code> as the parent.  Each section should have a title and horizontal rule.  Robot Web forms are normally inside a dialog panel region.</p>
    <div class="preview-section">
      <form class="form-content">
        <div class="form-section">
          <h4>Section Title</h4>
          <hr/>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="inputId">Label:</label>
            <input id="inputId" class="form-control" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="code-section">
                        <pre>
  &lt;form class=&quot;form-content&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;form-section&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h4&gt;Section Title&lt;/h4&gt;
  &lt;hr/&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;
    &lt;label for=&quot;inputId&quot;&gt;Label:&lt;/label&gt;
    &lt;input id=&quot;inputId&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; /&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/form&gt;
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
