  <div class="sg-section">
    <a name="standard-input"></a>
    <h2>Input Types</h2>
    <h3>Standard</h3>
    <p>We use standard HTML5 input types whenever we can.  Some input types are supported in all of our target browsers.  Others such as 'time' and 'date' are not supported in Firefox and IE.  For those we will need to use a webshim to bring in the functionality.</p>
    <div class="preview-section">
      <form class="form-content">
        <div class="form-section">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="textType">Text:</label>
            <input id="textType" name="textType" type="text" name="textType" class="form-control" placeholder="" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="textareaType">Textarea:</label>
            <textarea id="textareaType" name="textareaType" name="textareaType" class="form-control" placeholder="" ></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="selectType">Select:</label>
            <select id="selectType" name="selectType" name="selectType" class="form-control" placeholder="" >
              <option value="1">Option 1</option>
              <option value="2">Option 2</option>
              <option value="3">Option 3</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="numberType">Number:</label>
            <input id="numberType" name="numberType" type="number" name="numberType" class="form-control" placeholder="" min="0" max="200" step="10" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="dateType">Date (not supported in FF or IE):</label>
            <input id="dateType" name="dateType" type="date" name="dateType" class="form-control" placeholder="" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="timeType">Time (not supported in FF or IE):</label>
            <input id="timeType" name="timeType" type="time" name="timeType" class="form-control" placeholder="" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="code-section">
                        <pre>
